reviewText: Absolutely beautiful!! The niggunim were all beautifully sung and presented, and the entire video can be geared for children and adults, to enjoy the niggunim
My children loved it! I liked it too. Its very well made! Highly recommend.
awesome CD. My 2 year old sings the nigunim and even my older kids love it. Well done.
Awesome Keep up the great work of the REBBE

We just bought this dvd and my kids LOVE it! They've been watching it over and over back to back. This is entertaining and at the same time such a beautiful way to teach my children Niggunim of the Rebbe that we were brought up with as kids!
